$interpreted: Dylan: Who sent you?
Assassin: I don't know.
Dylan: For what purpose did you attempt to assassinate his Majesty Theodore?
Assassin: Do you really consider Theodore to be a good man?
Dylan: Cut the nonsense! Answer me!
Dylan: Let's start again. Who sent you?
Assassin: There are plenty of people out there who want Theodore dead...
Jahan: Don't you dare mention His Majesty's name!
Dylan: Let him go!
Assassin: Stay away; all I need is a quick snap of the neck and he is...
Jahan: NOooo~ don't do it! OUCH~ ouch~
Jahan: Whew, that was close...
Jahan: Again? Damnit!
Dylan: SPEAK! NOW! Who sent you!
Assassin: Hehe...he...you're quite good...
Dylan: Talk! Give me a name!
Assassin: However...Theodore...must pay...the price...*cough*...the wings of the Half-Blood...shall swipe away the imposter blocking the Sun!
Dylan: Poisoned himself...
Dylan: Go get a doctor.
Jahan: Y-Yes, sir! Doctor! Doctor!
Dylan: So no more clues left...wait, I can still investigate those last words he uttered.
Dylan: No one will be more familiar with the rebels' activities than those who also make a living underground.
Dylan: Seems that I have no choice but to turn every single gang hideout upside down until I find the mastermind behind all this!
